description: This file is a C header file containing function declarations pertaining to the exported API of the 'ansc_string_co' component. It defines prototypes for functions related to creating, removing, enrolling, and initializing the string component object, which suggests it provides an interface for string management within a broader system.

methods.name: AnscCreateStringComponent
methods.description: Creates an instance of the string component, accepting container, owner, and reserved handles.

methods.name: AnscStringCOCreate
methods.description: Creates an instance of the string component object.

methods.name: AnscStringCOEnrollObjects
